when you talk about it.

677
00:57:00,484 --> 00:57:01,902
I wonder why.

678
00:57:01,985 --> 00:57:03,570
Come here.

679
00:57:07,741 --> 00:57:09,618
- Right there.
- Here?

680
00:57:11,370 --> 00:57:14,706
I'm gonna ask you
a question, okay?

681
00:57:14,748 --> 00:57:17,042
Do you like cops?

682
00:57:17,126 --> 00:57:19,086
You're my first.

683
00:57:20,754 --> 00:57:24,133
